name: Senator Jar Jar Binks (AI)
Text: 'Agendas: justice, order. At same and related sites, vehicle weapon destiny draws are -2. Once per turn, may deploy an electropole, a [Coruscant] Naboo location, or a [Theed Palace] vehicle from Reserve Deck; reshuffle. If at Senate, may place Jar Jar and a [Coruscant] Political Effect out of play.(Original concept by Brian Herold - Minnesota States 2006)',
